criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Are aged from 5 to 14 years;

          2. To be in good general health;

          3. Written informed consent (by the child / parent)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Children who refuse to participate in the research; parents/guardians who refuse the
             participation of their children to the trial;

          2. Children who present systemic conditions or chronic diseases that require
             differentiated care and follow-up.
